WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.969
Hi, I just wanted to tell you another

00:00:01.979 --> 00:00:05.510
dream I had a while back that

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:07.490
I want to get out there. I want to get

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.950
this on the web to let people

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.930
pray over this. I don't know if this is

00:00:11.940 --> 00:00:13.970
during the tribulation that this happens

00:00:13.980 --> 00:00:15.890
or if this happens before the

00:00:15.900 --> 00:00:17.990
tribulation, but

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.910
you know, it's part of the birthing pains

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.470
that happen. In this dream,

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:27.349
there's a massive asteroid and it's

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:30.170
coming into the Earth. I see it

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:32.450
and everybody can see it, but you could

00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:35.450
hear it; it sounded like massive

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:38.630
freight trains. Everything

00:00:38.630 --> 00:00:38.640
was

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.209
shaking and moving so fast. I went

00:00:41.219 --> 00:00:43.729
outside in the dream and looked up, and

00:00:43.739 --> 00:00:46.310
it's just a massive streak of light, a

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:48.650
fireball coming out of the sky. It

00:00:48.660 --> 00:00:51.529
was moving so quick and so fast that it

00:00:51.539 --> 00:00:53.990
sounded like the whole earth was shaking.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.450
It was incredible; this thing

00:00:56.460 --> 00:01:00.709
was humongous. In the dream,

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:04.070
the United States tried to

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:07.370
shoot it down with a laser beam. It

00:01:07.380 --> 00:01:09.830
was moving too quick to shoot it down

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:12.590
with a rocket, so they used this laser

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.890
beam that, in my dream, was green. They

00:01:15.890 --> 00:01:15.900
hit

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:18.710
it with this laser weapon

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:22.130
and it split the rock. This

00:01:22.140 --> 00:01:25.910
massive asteroid split in two and

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:28.310
it busted up one half

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:31.070
into little bitty fragments, but the

00:01:31.080 --> 00:01:34.370
other half was still massive. It hit

00:01:34.380 --> 00:01:37.249
by the islands, by San Juan, Puerto

00:01:37.259 --> 00:01:41.090
Rico, and the Bahamas—all that

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:44.030
area out there. When it did, it

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:46.730
crashed into the ocean and created

00:01:46.740 --> 00:01:50.889
this massive tsunami. I'm talking

00:01:50.899 --> 00:01:55.069
humongous, like 100 feet up

00:01:55.079 --> 00:01:58.069
or more. It was moving so

00:01:58.079 --> 00:02:01.310
quick and so fast; it covered the islands

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:03.170
up. It covered Haiti;

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:03.180
it

00:02:03.180 --> 00:02:04.969
covered those things up.

00:02:04.979 --> 00:02:06.770
It just went over the top of

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:09.529
them. I could see it in the dream;

00:02:09.539 --> 00:02:11.869
these islands were just completely

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:14.449
engulfed with water.

00:02:14.459 --> 00:02:16.550
It went clear into Africa.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:19.130
When it came into

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:22.309
America, because it was so close, it hit

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:25.850
Miami, North Carolina, and South

00:02:25.850 --> 00:02:25.860
Carolina—all

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:28.070
that area.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:31.250
But the main area that I

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:33.530
was shown in the dream was the Miami

00:02:33.540 --> 00:02:36.470
area and Fort Lauderdale. It went

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:39.350
inland like the one that hit

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:40.550
Japan; the

00:02:40.550 --> 00:02:40.560
tsunami

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:43.369
wave

00:02:43.379 --> 00:02:45.170
washed in and

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:47.509
just wiped out houses

00:02:47.509 --> 00:02:47.519
and

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:49.729
buildings like they were nothing. It just

00:02:49.739 --> 00:02:52.729
blew them down. There

00:02:52.729 --> 00:02:52.739
were

00:02:52.739 --> 00:02:55.190
millions of people who were in

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:57.949
trouble and lost. Many were dead, and the

00:02:57.959 --> 00:03:00.710
Lord had me praying. When I woke up

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:02.930
the next day, He had me praying for these

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:05.930
people that they would hear Him and

00:03:05.930 --> 00:03:05.940
that

00:03:05.940 --> 00:03:07.550
they would not be there at that

00:03:07.550 --> 00:03:07.560
time—that

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:09.350
they would leave if this is

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:10.970
something that was going to happen soon.

00:03:10.980 --> 00:03:13.369
I don't know, but I prayed for these people

00:03:13.369 --> 00:03:13.379
so

00:03:13.379 --> 00:03:16.790
they would get out of harm's way.

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:19.850
It was just something that was very...

00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:22.729
when you wake up, you're in a

00:03:22.739 --> 00:03:25.729
cold sweat because it shook me. I

00:03:25.729 --> 00:03:25.739
was like,

00:03:25.739 --> 00:03:29.270
'Lord, I have to tell

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:30.949
people about this,'but I've just prayed

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:34.070
over it. I could

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.930
see that it was going to happen, and I don't

00:03:35.940 --> 00:03:37.850
know if we can stop it or

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:40.789
prevent it or whatever. I just felt in

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.309
my heart, this massive tsunami,

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:45.830
this massive asteroid coming out of the

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:48.470
sky. I've looked online at the

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:50.210
NASA site to see, but they

00:03:50.220 --> 00:03:52.250
didn't know this was coming. They didn't

00:03:52.260 --> 00:03:55.309
announce it on TV; they

00:03:55.319 --> 00:03:57.410
didn't tell people that it was coming. It

00:03:57.420 --> 00:03:59.509
just happened and, like I

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:02.809
said, it was humongous. It flew in and

00:04:02.819 --> 00:04:04.970
hit out there in the ocean, in

00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:08.390
the Atlantic. It caused

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:10.910
devastation worldwide. I

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:12.410
don't know if this is the Tribulation the Lord

00:04:12.410 --> 00:04:12.420
is

00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:14.690
showing me, or if it's something

00:04:14.700 --> 00:04:16.969
that happens in the birthing pains, but

00:04:16.979 --> 00:04:18.469
it's just one of the things I felt like

00:04:18.479 --> 00:04:20.390
I should share that the Lord has

00:04:20.390 --> 00:04:20.400
shown

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:23.330
me. Thank you very much for watching. There

00:04:23.330 --> 00:04:23.340
are

00:04:23.340 --> 00:04:24.530
other things that the Lord

00:04:24.540 --> 00:04:25.969
showed me, and I'm going to tell those in

00:04:25.979 --> 00:04:27.770
other videos. Have a blessed

00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:30.020
day. Bye.

